Changes from 0.10.0 to 0.11.0 - released 2012/1/11

*General:

*Bugfixes:

- when using basic auth, part of the request http headers were being dropped

*Incompatible changes

- the error code generated by the clients(s) when receiving http status codes
  other than 20x has changed from ERROR_BAD_RESPONSE to a more specific one:
  ERROR_NON_200_RESPONSE (the former is used for all responses not complying
  with the http spec)
